---
title: Old-School BBQ Pork Sloppy Joes with Pickled Onion, Potato Wedges & Chipotle Ranch
description: The humble sloppy Joe may be one of the most underrated comfort foods. Adults and kids alike will love this version, which has a few flavor upgrades that take it to the next level. Onion and ground pork are browned, then simmered with barbecue sauce spiked with a little chipotle powder for a smoky kick. The filling’s stuffed between potato buns with pickled onion for tang and served with roasted potato wedges on the side. Tasty nostalgia on the table in just 25 minutes? It doesn’t get much better than that.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/63592c7230a8b6e83d035c79-89d937b2.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/old-school-bbq-pork-sloppy-joes-63592c7230a8b6e83d035c79-33bde6be.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/old-school-bbq-pork-sloppy-joes-63592c7230a8b6e83d035c79
author: HelloFresh
servings: 2
course: main course
time required: 35 minutes
cuisine: North America
nutrition:
  calories: 980 kcal
  fat: 47 g
